                <p style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><span style=";">гражданин Республики Казахстан,</span></p>
                <p style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><span style=";">____________________________________________________________________________</span></p>
                <p style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;text-align:center;'><em><span
                            style=";color:#548DD4;">(<span style="color:#0A46C8;"><span
