                        style=";">______</span><span style=";">_ 20__г.</span></p>
                <p style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><em><span
                            style=";color:#548DD4;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (дата)</span></em></p>
                <p style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><span style=";">&nbsp;_________________________________________________&nbsp;</span></p>
                <p style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><em><span
                            style=";color:#548DD4;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;(подпись)</span></em></p>
                <p style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><span style=";">__________________________________________________________________________________</span></p>
                <p style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'><em><span
